Knowledge is power, and in America, that power belongs to the people. Let’s CLEAR things up:

Today, I’m introducing the CLEAR Act  — Consistent Legal Expectations and Access to Records — to ensure that Americans know how every government agency is spending their tax dollars. No matter if an agency exists for one month or one hundred years, it shouldn’t be exempt from FOIA requests.

@GerryConnolly, @CongressMin, and @RepKweisiMfume have joined me as co-leads on this legislation. Democrat or Republican, we must ensure we’re holding our government accountable to the American taxpayers. Read more here. https://t.co/z4kg8Jeb6M
